-- Podravka, Atlantic May Share Distribution, Poslovni Says
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-11-09T07:19:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-09/podravka-atlantic-may-share-distribution-poslovni-says.html
Podravka Prehrambena Industrija d.d. ,
 Croatia ’s second-largest food producer, and  Atlantic Grupa d.d .,
may share product distribution abroad,  Poslovni Dnevnik 
reported, citing unidentified Atlantic officials.  Atlantic, a Zagreb-based food producer and retailer, may
take over the distribution of Podravka products in Serbia and
Macedonia, while Podravka may do the same for Atlantic’s
products in  Poland , according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  